{"tid":1565623,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【 突發】第二輪炮火！行動升級！除咗取消港共外國護照，我地正式開辟聯合國人道罪行戰線！(2)","createTime":"2019-09-13T08:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T14:09:35.000Z","uid":70964,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"79a3a3110aa1b5c1eeba9a4f61301dd00b016400","tid":1565623,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:30:27.000Z","msg":"(舊貼推爆左)<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1217474/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1217474/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n生死存亡之秋，請各位爭取解鎖1001。<br />\n<br />\n致各位真正香港人、傳媒、連登仔：<br />\n<br />\n大家撐住！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼第一波攻勢正式去信英美澳 &mdash;&mdash; 熱心幫港共官員、保皇黨同佢地家人取消外國護照、凍結資產，我地決定將行動升級，徹查港共同香港警察涉嫌嚴重違反國際人權公約。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n動用過份武力、圍毆被捕市民、襲擊記者、涉嫌阻止救護車救人，全部都係嚴重人道公約！<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，我地人力減半情況下依然趕起咗第二波法理分析、整理香港失控警察違反國際人權公約証據，起草信件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n謹此宣布相關舉報信件已經正式送達聯合國 人權高級專員辦事處，要求聯合國介入事件，打擊港共及警察失控追打香港市民、阻礙人道救援，同襲擊世界各地記者！<br />\n<br />\n已發出信件例子如下：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1IDa69eAECjsndciORVMt3pWA0hIIBUmT/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1IDa69eAECjsndciORVMt3pWA0hIIBUmT%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=1ded932b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1IDa69eAECjsndciORVMt3pWA0hIIBUmT/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更重要係，我地誠邀睇到依個post既人下載以下pdf，一齊幫手forward上面既聯合國信件到各大組織同校友會，拜託佢地幫手提交我地預備既聯合國信件 &mdash;&mdash; 全力增加聯合國回應既機會，等聯合國關注香港有多達三萬失控警察！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講就係：<br />\n你 -&gt; 各大組織 -&gt; 聯合國<br />\n<br />\n呼籲轉載PDF：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/12bm6lV5hK10cop6z9AbgtqnJy0D8kOWG/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F12bm6lV5hK10cop6z9AbgtqnJy0D8kOWG%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=e5ba4f80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/12bm6lV5hK10cop6z9AbgtqnJy0D8kOWG/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各大友好組織名單：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/12bm6lV5hK10cop6z9AbgtqnJy0D8kOWG/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F12bm6lV5hK10cop6z9AbgtqnJy0D8kOWG%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=e5ba4f80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/12bm6lV5hK10cop6z9AbgtqnJy0D8kOWG/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，我地亦都非常高興同大家講，美國國會多名議員決定聯手推動《香港人權與民主法案》。一旦通過，將會立即禁止港共官員及保皇黨踏足美國領土，凍結在美資產。共享大灣區榮耀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一則好消息係，前港督彭定康先生已經親自回應我地第一波攻勢信件，作出跟進！<br />\n<br />\n我地爭取緊彭督同意我地公開相關回覆，現階段我地至少可以簡略轉述彭督正接觸英國外相 Jeremy Hunt 討論香港情況。當彭督有新消息，就會通知我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n此外，我地現正同大量，重申係大量，在英港人合縱連橫，嘗試親身約見第一波攻勢提到既18位英國國會議員。暫時已經得到下議院Catherine West MP 同 Lucas Caroline MP回覆跟進！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於送中條例仍然苟延殘喘，我地亦決定即時將港共官員-保皇黨-警隊共享大灣區榮譽計劃升級至第三波。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎緊我地會著手研究加拿大、北歐四國以及歐盟對港共官員、保皇黨、警察實拖Travel Ban 之可行性。同時進一步同在英港人會師，嘗試接觸英國政府、國會。<br />\n<br />\n我地謹此呼籲大家share 依個Post到fb各大媒體、甚至放落保皇黨fb page同幫港出聲fb 正面挑機，加強施壓！[/b]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[b]香港人唔好放棄！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gu8eoN1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGu8eoN1.png&h=e7f1806b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yC2CmzN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyC2CmzN.png&h=a666cc87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【 突發】正式開火！第一批信已發出！我地香港人要幫政府官員、保皇黨取消外國護照！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1204306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1204306</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n生死存亡之秋，請各位爭取解鎖1001。"},{"pid":"1d4e789674c04f05742e71943fd4ef59805f57c9","tid":1565623,"uid":252660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:30:55.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0523fd4afb546c367f55d5c9588237ecb4f278d","tid":1565623,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31c089cebb526ae4a25f3d41423059c43c8714a","tid":1565623,"uid":141097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714b859f170dc106e77451e1dacde6478cc48beb","tid":1565623,"uid":124330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:44:39.000Z","msg":"推呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6235a1572999a56bb9adb28e5f30d45c4fd01ca2","tid":1565623,"uid":72253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:49:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5789734fc6a0dd8b39724ba4977c2f486bf56851","tid":1565623,"uid":8562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:02:22.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a01cd71c845f9374b4aaf5bc470e72a2abe05ca2","tid":1565623,"uid":297666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:03:13.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a15e5a246cd9bb22e93000910e053c8239ba5a90","tid":1565623,"uid":